name: GAL XLOKK Foundation
goal: THE GAL XLOKK Foundation is one of the three local action groups in Malta. It is responsible for the LEADER programme (2014-2020) as part of the South east Local development strategy in the Maltese Islands.
interests: Agriculture, Education and training, Environment, Trans-European Networks
euInitiatives: The Foundation is responsible for the LEADER programme (2014-2020). The Foundation will be issuing a number of action as part of the South east local development strategy.
